This is Perl module Dancer::Template::MicroTemplateExtended.

INSTALLATION

Dancer::Template::MicroTemplateExtended installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Dancer::Template::MicroTemplateExtended

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Dancer::Template::MicroTemplateExtended documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Dancer::Template::MicroTemplateExtended

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.
